    "name": "Pine Hearts",
    "steam_appid": 1781010,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险在等待着你！和泰克一起踏上舒适的徒步探险之旅，前往广袤的松心自然保护区，攀登父亲从未征服的那座高山。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越岩石水潭，探索神秘洞穴，清理露营地，调查古老城堡废墟，在海滩上尽情玩耍，泰克将重温童年假期的场景，回忆与父亲共度的冒险时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/7a8952c2c0acc4e6dad46c79754e1bfe.poster.avif?t=1763465088\" width=800 height=494 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/7a8952c2c0acc4e6dad46c79754e1bfe.webm?t=1763465088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/7a8952c2c0acc4e6dad46c79754e1bfe.mp4?t=1763465088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >松心自然保护区是一片迷人的世界，纵横交错的小路和捷径遍布其间，处处充满奇妙的互动。结交众多新朋友，为需要帮助的当地人完成各种有趣的任务，包括：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >担任蔬菜比赛评委！🥕</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指挥铜管乐队！🎺</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帮助幽灵！👻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重建观鲸船！🐋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救迷途蜜蜂！🐝</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >布置（相机）陷阱捕捉怪物！📸</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挖掘维京宝藏！👑</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸在这个充满回忆的迷人世界中，为你遇到的每个人创造一段难忘的假期回忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/36c94d90fd8262ea4457a56cfff26c1c.poster.avif?t=1763465088\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/36c94d90fd8262ea4457a56cfff26c1c.webm?t=1763465088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/36c94d90fd8262ea4457a56cfff26c1c.mp4?t=1763465088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>感人至深的家庭失落故事</strong>——温暖而细腻的故事，讲述泰克缅怀已故父亲的点点滴滴，用温柔和关怀娓娓道来</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>阳光明媚的苏格兰背景</strong>——探索一个相互连通的世界，灵感来自我们童年时期前往苏格兰高地凯恩戈姆山度假的经历。还有艺术加工，让这里阳光明媚</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不只是公园</strong>——前往松心自然保护区的探险者将邂逅沙滩、尘土飞扬的地下墓穴、郁郁葱葱的高尔夫球场以及热闹的旅行拖车公园等地点</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松解谜，无压力探索</strong>——按照自己的节奏解锁装备和能力，开辟捷径，探索银河恶魔城风格地图的新区域</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>异想天开的角色和任务</strong>——结交新朋友，为他们做好事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>撸可爱的狗狗 🐶 </strong>——我们通过了@CanYouPetTheDog（可以撸狗狗嘛）知名账号认证</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>拍可爱的螃蟹 🦀 </strong>——如果存在@CanYouPatTheCrab（可以拍蟹蟹嘛）账号，我们也会通过认证的</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>甜蜜沉思时刻</strong>——坐在长椅上休息片刻，欣赏美景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全面的无障碍选项</strong>——简化控制、色彩分区、黑白和高对比度模式、视觉特效切换、字体缩放、全键位自定义等等</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Pine Hearts》是寻求放松和直观冒险体验玩家的完美选择，探索大自然，与可爱的角色建立联系，创造超越生命的家庭回忆。游戏灵感来自我们自己的经历，献给那些在旅途中与我们一同珍藏回忆的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/cce701d3831d8677a9205af78f0bbb21.avif?t=1763465088\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p>",
